{"parentUuid":null,"isSidechain":true,"promptId":"344fc92d-6e78-4e50-be34-264d4cf2af1f","agentId":"a028d2afca704182a","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"You are implementing Task 3 of the project-reader plugin Phase 2.\n\n## Context\n\nPlugin location: `~/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader/`\n\nThis is a Claude Code plugin for multi-language project analysis. Phase 2 adds call chain tracing. This task creates the `/trace` slash command that users will invoke.\n\n**Role**: User entry point → cache check → call project-detector → call trace-executor → display results\n\n## Your Task\n\nCreate: `~/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader/commands/trace.md`\n\nWrite this file using the Write tool with EXACTLY this content:\n\n---\ndescription: 追踪指定符号的调用链，支持跨语言穿透（Swift→OC→C++），结果缓存到 ~/.claude/analyses/<key>/CALL_CHAINS/。\nargument-hint: \"<symbol> [--refresh] [--depth N] [--inbound]\"\n---\n\n# /trace — 调用链追踪\n\n## 参数说明\n\n- `<symbol>`（必填）：要追踪的符号名。支持：\n  - 函数/方法名：`viewDidLoad`、`application:didFinishLaunchingWithOptions:`\n  - 类名：`AudioEngine`（追踪该类的 init 方法及主要公开方法）\n  - 通知名：`NSNotification.Name.audioDidStop`（触发 Notification 映射模式）\n  - Router URL：`/home/tab`（触发 Router 解析模式）\n- `--refresh`：强制重新追踪，忽略已有缓存\n- `--depth N`：最大追踪深度（默认 15；`--depth 0` 表示不限深度，为特殊值，慎用）\n- `--inbound`：反向追踪——找谁调用了目标符号（默认向下追踪调用链）\n\n## 执行流程\n\n### Step 1: 解析参数\n\n从 `$ARGUMENTS` 中提取：\n- `symbol` = 第一个非 `--` 开头的参数\n- `refresh` = 包含 `--refresh`\n- `depth` = `--depth` 后的数字（默认 15）\n- `inbound` = 包含 `--inbound`\n\n若无 `symbol`，输出「用法：/trace <symbol> [--refresh] [--depth N] [--inbound]」并停止。\n\n### Step 2: 语言检测\n\n调用 `project-detector` agent 获取 `lang_result`（含语言类型、混编信息、project_root）。\n\n### Step 3: 计算 project_key 和缓存路径\n\n使用 Bash 计算 project_key：\n```bash\npython3 -c \"\nimport hashlib, os\ncwd = os.getcwd()\nname = os.path.basename(cwd)\nh = hashlib.md5(cwd.encode()).hexdigest()[:8]\nprint(f'{name}-{h}')\n\"\n```\n\n构造 symbol_slug：将 symbol 名称中的特殊字符（空格、冒号、括号、点）替换为下划线，保留原始大小写。\n\n构造缓存文件路径：\n```\n~/.claude/analyses/<project_key>/CALL_CHAINS/<symbol_slug>.md\n```\n\n使用 Glob 检查缓存是否存在：\n- 存在且无 `--refresh` → 使用 Read 读取缓存，输出内容，提示「使用缓存。运行 /trace <symbol> --refresh 强制更新」\n- 不存在或有 `--refresh` → 继续执行追踪\n\n### Step 4: 执行追踪\n\n调用 `trace-executor` agent，传入：\n- `symbol`（Step 1 解析结果）\n- `project_key`（Step 3 计算结果）\n- `project_root`（来自 lang_result.project_root）\n- `lang_result`（project-detector 的 JSON 输出）\n- `depth`（Step 1 解析结果，默认 15）\n- `direction`（`inbound` if --inbound else `outbound`）\n\n### Step 5: 输出\n\ntrace-executor 完成后，显示调用链结果并提示：\n```\n💾 结果已保存：~/.claude/analyses/<project_key>/CALL_CHAINS/<symbol_slug>.md\n运行 /trace <symbol> --refresh 重新追踪\n```\n\n## 约束\n\n- 不修改目标项目任何文件\n- 追踪结果只写入 `~/.claude/analyses/`\n- 第三方库（Pods/、.build/）符号标注后不穿透\n- 动态调用（OC runtime、C++ 虚函数）标注后停止，不猜测\n\n## Steps\n\n1. Write the file to `~/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader/commands/trace.md` using the Write tool.\n\n2. Verify frontmatter:\n```bash\nhead -5 ~/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader/commands/trace.md\n```\nExpected: `description` and `argument-hint` fields present.\n\n3. Verify the command has all required flags documented:\n```bash\ngrep -n \"\\-\\-refresh\\|\\-\\-depth\\|\\-\\-inbound\\|depth.*15\\|默认 15\" ~/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader/commands/trace.md\n```\nExpected: all 3 flags and default depth=15 are mentioned.\n\n4. Commit:\n```bash\ncd ~/.claude/plugins/local/project-reader\ngit add commands/trace.md\ngit commit -m \"feat: add /trace command with cache support and depth/direction options\"\n```\n\n## Self-Review Checklist\n- [ ] File at `commands/trace.md`\n- [ ] frontmatter: description + argument-hint\n- [ ] Step 1: parses symbol, --refresh, --depth, --inbound from $ARGUMENTS\n- [ ] Step 1: handles missing symbol gracefully\n- [ ] Step 2: calls project-detector agent\n- [ ] Step 3: Python MD5 hash for project_key\n- [ ] Step 3: cache hit path (read + hint)\n- [ ] Step 3: cache miss/refresh path (continue)\n- [ ] Step 4: calls trace-executor with all 6 parameters\n- [ ] 